<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2011-05-03</DATELINE><TITLE>Parasites and Their World Records in Their Fight for Survival</TITLE><BODY>Parasites are animals that enter plants, animals and humans – but are not welcome. Therefore they had to develop strategies for invasion and survival – outside and inside of hosts. For this purpose they developed amazing, often unbelievable skills during evolution. Thirteen of them are presented in this chapter showing that they are fit for the future thus threatening mankind, if there are no precautions in the future.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>